      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i've been noticing something really weird with my smart thermostat and my fridge lately. every time i get really stressed or angry, the thermostat temperature just... shifts. like it drops a few degrees right when i'm upset. and my fridge makes this specific humming sound too. is there some kind of way these things could be sensing my mood or something? it's starting to feel intentional.",
