    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a coincidence tho. i've been tracking it. last tuesday i was having a huge argument on the phone and the temp dropped immediately. like, within seconds. and the fridge hum is different too... it's like it's syncing up with the thermostat. i know it sounds crazy but i feel like they're talking to each other. is there any actual tech that would allow them to communicate or pass data like that?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
